Hey! I'm Jessica and I'm currently a junior studying Computer Science at the University of Southern California (USC). 

I'm a software engineer with an interest in entrepreneurship and web development. I'm also hoping to get into and learn cybersecurity in the near future.

In my free time, I like to bake, cook, and scuba dive. Outside of school, I also enjoy going to hackathons and coming up with and creating things on the fly. If you ever want to work together, feel free to reach out to me!
